             was indicted for <rs id="t18180218-71-off376" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18180218-71-off376" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180218-71-off376" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
